pannweite von experimenteller Phonetik, über quantitative Linguistik und Analysen von Einzelsprachen bis hin zu großangelegten typologischen Vergleichen.  aMode of access: Internet via World Wide Web.  aIn English.0 aDescription based on online resource; title from PDF title page (publisher's Web site, viewed 17. Dez 2021) 4aEinsilber. 4aMonosyllaba. 4aPhonetik. 4aTypologie. 7aLANGUAGE ARTS & DISCIPLINES / Linguistics / General.2bisacsh1 aBasbøll, Hans, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aChen, Yuan-Lu, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aDreer, Igor, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aFloricic, Franck, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aHauser, Sonja, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aMichaud, Alexis, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aMolinu, Lucia, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aNau, Nicole, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aNau, Nicole, eeditor.4edt4http://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/edt1 aOrzechowska, Paula, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aSo, Connie K., econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aStamer, Heiko, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aSteiner, Petra, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aStolz, Thomas, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aStolz, Thomas, eeditor.4edt4http://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/edt1 aStroh, Cornelia, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aStroh, Cornelia, eeditor.4edt4http://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/edt1 aZerbian, Sabine, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb08iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertDGBA B